title: Hi Res MtG Card Scans from mtgimage.com
description:
This torrent contains a couple of downloads (AllSetsWindows.hq.zip as of 2015-03-02) from mtgimage.com, a site that was shut down by WotC's lawyers (shit be upon them) on 2015-03-10. They contain high resolution scans of all Magic: The Gathering cards in the collection up to that time.

I haven't created a torrent in a long time so apologies in advance if this one isn't set up correctly; if it isn't, let me know in the comments and I will keep trying until I get it right
